
Exploud	 A normal type Pokémon

EXPLOUD triggers earthquakes with the 
tremors it creates by bellowing.  If 
this POKéMON violently inhales from the 
ports on its body, it’s a sign that it 
is preparing to let loose a huge bellow. 

